  "texts": [
    "The responses were given on a 5-point Likert scale: \"I strongly disagree, \" \"I disagree, \" \"Neutral, \" \"I agree, \" and \"I strongly agree. \"",
    "The questionnaire was reviewed by faculty from engineering, statistics, and medicine backgrounds and was e-mailed to the participants.",
    "InterviewExperts among the researchers prepared four openended questions for the participants who had already completed the questionnaire.",
    "The queries were revised after a pilot interview with a small group of students.",
    "Two groups were determined and selected by a simple random method, structured as one student from each field, adding up to eight participants."
  ],
